2. `.trae/documents/` (if applicable)
3. `.trae/adr/README.md` (add ADR number)

## Single-Sentence Summary

> Core is "layered + modularized": business logic in services, data access via repositories, routes do validation+forward only. New feature: migration → repository → service → routes → frontend API → frontend page (6 steps).
